{"tid":1085554,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"【雙語談戀愛】女就男講國語 Stephy投訴王子：淨係識得叫嘢食","createTime":"2019-03-31T08:35:23.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-01T00:12:00.000Z","uid":130626,"like":2,"dislike":19,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"dd9c241a30ffdc225daae364320fabf9b986e2d6","tid":1085554,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-31T08:35:23.000Z","msg":"鄧麗欣（Stephy）今早在山頂支持慈善跑活動，同場參與跑手還有吳雲甫、郭思琳、董嘉儀，可惜Stephy因工作關係，未能落場參與，她說雖然每次都是大清早時分舉行，但樂於參與慈善。<br />\n完成上一部電影作品後，Stephy希望盡快物色到新角色，現有幾個劇本洽談中，她表示自己對角色持開放態度，但近日突然想挑戰懸疑角色，不過劇本未夠張力，要調節做到最好。<br />\n此外，Stephy和台灣男友王子（邱勝翊）公開戀情後感情穩定，問到工作上可以情侶檔上陣？Stephy坦言：「暫時又冇喎，賺錢OK嘅，睇吓點做法，費事俾人話我太高調，適可而止就可以。」維持異地戀要經常港台兩邊飛，Stephy樂做跟得女友：「OK啦，唔喺香港當然辛苦少少，識好多朋友long distance仲遠，英國同加拿大嗰啲仲慘，我起碼冇時差。」Stephy透露近日王子正在開工拍劇，笑言：「呢段時間要我遷就佢多啲，到我忙時佢都會過香港，睇情況。」<br />\n而港、台兩地語言溝通雖然不成障礙，但就搞到Stephy有時難以觸摸：「內地同台灣國語唔同，有時都搞到我個tone會亂咗，不過平時都係我講國語就佢多，佢唔會講廣東話，太難喇，佢又少睇港劇，佢淨係識得叫嘢食。」傳媒取笑至少應該會識「我愛你」三個字，Stephy大笑指可能識講粗口先，但從沒教過男友。<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190331/large/1554016314_6dc1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190331%2Flarge%2F1554016314_6dc1.jpg&h=23c649c8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190331/large/1554016314_0227.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190331%2Flarge%2F1554016314_0227.jpg&h=dc3f2936&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190331/large/1554016316_6c19.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190331%2Flarge%2F1554016316_6c19.jpg&h=2e0795bf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/enews/realtime/article/20190331/59433326\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fenews%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190331%2F59433326&d=Sk6y7wLkZ8LsH37jlkaP94Lj0gigvT8yTat38OYNh6E%3D&h=e1ce3a37\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fenews%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190331%2F59433326&h=e746485f\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/enews/realtime/article/20190331/59433326</a>"},{"pid":"841149a7db95df64f76ea920b0275ff45b26b107","tid":1085554,"uid":66945,"like":11,"dislike":12,"score":-1,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-03-31T08:40:59.000Z","msg":"stephy個樣真係好青春<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"006512d372b39ac190326bad3c591a2555e16f16","tid":1085554,"uid":217214,"like":9,"dislike":6,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-31T08:52:10.000Z","msg":"一睇就知王子明顯係玩玩下啦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"713f859419cd7cb456ae1f00c35cbad9e3c6ebbd","tid":1085554,"uid":139974,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-31T08:54:59.000Z","msg":"送外賣送到台灣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"264f0cb0a47a03c1dcf338bc56995fed2dc17260","tid":1085554,"uid":152123,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"quote":{"pid":"841149a7db95df64f76ea920b0275ff45b26b107","tid":1085554,"uid":66945,"like":11,"dislike":12,"score":-1,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-03-31T08:40:59.000Z","msg":"stephy個樣真係好青春<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-31T10:41:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://s2.gifyu.com/images/2019_03_27_06_14_48.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fs2.gifyu.com%2Fimages%2F2019_03_27_06_14_48.gif&h=f2ab3936&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"31440f3b92fcec4cbc0a654b5d6f9613461d6e49","tid":1085554,"uid":22210,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-31T12:28:56.000Z","msg":"狗宮格巴打呢?"},{"pid":"1247969360fd0b38